rt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 3733, \"end\": 3741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Sport\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"over 1,000 elite athletes\", \"from\": 3704, \"to\": 3729}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 3829, \"to\": 3835}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's best coaches\", \"from\": 3839, \"to\": 3863}, {\"ngram\": \"benefit\", \"from\": 3868, \"to\": 3875}, {\"ngram\": \"medical support\", \"from\": 3892, \"to\": 3907}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Paris, McGowan will compete alongside her boyfriend and two-time world champion Bradly Sinden, who won silver in Tokyo, as well as fellow Olympic newcomer and housemate Caden Cunningham.\", \"from\": 3910, \"to\": 4099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3913, \"end\": 3918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999722604, \"rank\": 2.7823585241138424e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3920, \"end\": 3927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.602444570168454, \"rank\": 0.6599037480011448, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\"}, {\"begin\": 4026, \"end\": 4031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9949698170644153, \"rank\": 0.0050554482979375094, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 4088, \"end\": 4098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bri