wan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a nice house\", \"from\": 4315, \"to\": 4327}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a good house to be in.\", \"from\": 4384, \"to\": 4411, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good house\", \"from\": 4389, \"to\": 4401}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are all in the excited phase, all ready to be there and embrace it all.\", \"from\": 4412, \"to\": 4486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the excited phase\", \"from\": 4426, \"to\": 4443}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's quite a high-energy house.\\\"\", \"from\": 4487, \"to\": 4519, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"quite a high-energy house\", \"from\": 4492, \"to\": 4517}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As with many taekwondo athletes, McGowan has suffered her fair share of injuries, including a pair of broken ribs just a fortnight before she claimed her World Championship silver medal.\", \"from\": 4521, \"to\": 4707, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4554, \"end\": 4561, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.602444570168454, \"rank\": 0.6599037480011448, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many taekwondo athletes\", \"from\": 4529, \"to\": 4552}, {\"ngram\": \"her fair share\", \"from\": 4575, \"to\": 4589}, {\"ngram\": \"injuries\", \"from\": 4593, \"to\": 4601}, {\"ngram\": \"a pair\", \"from\": 4613, \"to\": 4619}, {\"ngram\": \"broken ribs\", \"from\": 4623, \"to\": 4634}, {\"ngram\": \"her World Championship silver medal\", \"from\": 4671, \"to\": 4706}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But with the Olympics now just around the corner, McGowan is doing everything to ensure she arrives in France in the best possible shape.\", \"from\": 4709, \"to\": 4846, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4759, \"end\": 4766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.602444570168454, \"rank\": 0.6599037480011448, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\"}, {\"begin\": 4812, \"end\": 4818, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6692423403954273, \"rank\": 0.4941841237939242, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4718, \"to\": 4730}, {\"ngram\": \"the corner\", \"from\": 4747, \"to\": 4757}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 4776, \"to\": 4786}, {\"ngram\": \"the best possible shape\", \"from\": 4822, \"to\": 4845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"I am feeling good, I am feeling the best I have felt for a long time.\", \"from\": 4848, \"to\": 4928, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 4916, \"to\": 4927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have already started our prep camp, we have got training partners over.\", \"from\": 4930, \"to\": 5005, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our prep camp\", \"from\": 4955, \"to\": 4968}, {\"ngram\": \"training partners\", \"from\": 4982, \"to\": 4999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are in the deep of it right now.\", \"from\": 5006, \"to\": 5041, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the deep\", \"from\": 5016, \"to\": 5024}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are just continuing on with that, ironing everything out, making sure that everything is as good as it can be.\", \"from\": 5043, \"to\": 5157, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 5089, \"to\": 5099}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 5122, \"to\": 5132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We want to make sure we are even more beasts for Paris.\", \"from\": 5158, \"to\": 5213, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5207, \"end\": 5212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999722604, \"rank\": 2.7823585241138424e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"even more beasts\", \"from\": 5186, \"to\": 5202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are training a lot.\", \"from\": 5215, \"to\": 5238, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For me it has to be smart training.\", \"from\": 5239, \"to\": 5274, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"smart training\", \"from\": 5259, \"to\": 5273}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the injuries I have carried, I train a bit smarter, if I have only got so many sessions, I have got to make the most of everyone.\", \"from\": 5275, \"to\": 5409, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the injuries\", \"from\": 5280, \"to\": 5292}, {\"ngram\": \"so many sessions\", \"from\": 5351, \"to\": 5367}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 5400, \"to\": 5408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not let any time slide.\", \"from\": 5410, \"to\": 5439, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have got to make the most of every session.\\\"\", \"from\": 5440, \"to\": 5486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every session\", \"from\": 5471, \"to\": 5484}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McGowan will compete on the final Saturday of the Games, along with Cunningham, knowing that her entire Olympic dream rests entirely on a single day.\", \"from\": 5488, \"to\": 5637, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5488, \"end\": 5495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.602444570168454, \"rank\": 0.6599037480011448, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\"}, {\"begin\": 5556, \"end\": 5566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"score\": 0.9999354009275992, \"rank\": 6.425160858601735e-05, \"text\": \"Cunningham\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Briggs_Cunningham\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the final Saturday\", \"from\": 5512, \"to\": 5530}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 5534, \"to\": 5543}, {\"ngram\": \"her entire Olympic dream\", \"from\": 5581, \"to\": 5605}, {\"ngram\": \"a single day\", \"from\": 5624, \"to\": 5636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But rather than worry about what might happen if she is not at her best on the day, McGowan is going to seize an opportunity.\", \"from\": 5639, \"to\": 5764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5723, \"end\": 5730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"score\": 0.602444570168454, \"rank\": 0.6599037480011448, \"text\": \"McGowan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_McGowan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 5714, \"to\": 5721}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 5749, \"to\": 5763}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She concluded: \\\"It's something that is inevitable, you will think about it.\", \"from\": 5766, \"to\": 5841, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 5787, \"to\": 5796}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's four years' worth of work for one day.\", \"from\": 5842, \"to\": 5885, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"four years' worth\", \"from\": 5847, \"to\": 5864}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 5868, \"to\": 5872}, {\"ngram\": \"one day\", \"from\": 5877, \"to\": 5884}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I have tried to switch my thought process around it.\", \"from\": 5886, \"to\": 5942, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my thought process\", \"from\": 5913, \"to\": 5931}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hopefully, it could be done in six minutes, so give everything you can in those six minutes.\", \"from\": 5943, \"to\": 6035, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"six minutes\", \"from\": 5974, \"to\": 5985}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 5995, \"to\": 6005}, {\"ngram\": \"those six minutes\", \"from\": 6017, \"to\": 6034}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And then you could walk away Olympic champion.\\\"\", \"from\": 6036, \"to\": 6083, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic champion\", \"from\": 6065, \"to\": 6081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"National Lottery players raise more than \\u00a330million a week for good causes including vital funding into sport - from grassroots to elite.\", \"from\": 6085, \"to\": 6222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6085, \"end\": 6101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"score\": 0.9999999941942406, \"rank\": 5.79756330463472e-09, \"text\": \"National Lottery\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"good causes\", \"from\": 6148, \"to\": 6159}, {\"ngram\": \"vital funding\", \"from\": 6170, \"to\": 6183}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 6189, \"to\": 6194}, {\"ngram\": \"grassroots\", \"from\": 6202, \"to\": 6212}, {\"ngram\": \"elite\", \"from\": 6216, \"to\": 6221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To find out more visit:www.lotterygoodcauses.org.uk#TNLAthletes Impartial news + intelligent debate